    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, offering a reliable driving experience for its next owner. The exterior is clean and presents well, though you will find some minor signs of use such as small stone chips and light surface scratches. Inside, the cabin is tidy and comfortable, with only light wear on the upholstery and controls. Mechanically, it remains sound and performs as expected, making it a dependable choice for anyone seeking a quality used vehicle.",
