    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended primarily for parts or as a major restoration project. The exterior has significant damage, including heavy rust on the rocker panels, large dents on the rear quarter panel, and severely oxidized paint. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears, and the electronics are inconsistent. Mechanically, the engine runs but has a noticeable knock and requires immediate attention to the transmission and braking system. It is being sold strictly as-is; please bring a trailer as it is not currently roadworthy.",
