      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a basic set of wheels to get you from A to B? This vehicle is in poor condition and definitely shows its age with significant wear and tear, but it's a great opportunity for someone handy or looking for a bargain! It's an honest car with a lot of character, ready for a new owner who isn't afraid of a little work.",
